1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with depth and optical flow estimation from stereo videos using deep neural networks. 
2. cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper mentions camera ego-motion estimation, which is relevant to robotics. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper uses deep neural networks for learning. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper deals with intelligent systems that can learn from visual data. 
5. cs.CVPR (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is another possible category as the paper deals with computer vision tasks such as depth and optical flow estimation.
